This is a simple yet functional Timer App built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides a Pomodoro-style countdown timer with different modes, including:

Pomodoro Mode (25 min)

Short Break (5 min)

Long Break (15 min)

The app allows users to start, pause, reset, and stop the timer. When the countdown reaches zero, an audio alert is played.

Features

1. Start, stop, and reset the timer
2. Display countdown in minutes and seconds
3. Switch between Short Break, and Long Break modes
4. Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop


Tech Stack

HTML → For structuring the app

CSS → For styling and responsiveness

JavaScript → For timer functionality

